{"tid":1658820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(有片) 觀塘站放火單case連登仔可能炒咗車","createTime":"2019-10-16T15:38:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T16:38:48.000Z","uid":123613,"like":3,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"dcf261c38681779ab5eae50c02122ab7184c0b8d","tid":1658820,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T15:38:59.000Z","msg":"相關討論：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1627598/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1627598/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1628938/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1628938/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n4號晚有人影咗觀塘站月台有popo： <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2lGiw2rfHWI&amp;t=3s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2lGiw2rfHWI%26t%3D3s&d=Wg3pkMW64ksxbb%2FAt9Sry%2BxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=3a782ced\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2lGiw2rfHWI&amp;t=3s</a><br />\n連登之前話觀塘站燶晒係因為popo放火，4號晚拍片者拍片嗰陣九龍灣站開始封，唔停牛頭角，條片最後幾秒到觀塘站，2:49影到去黃埔個月台有車開住門運popo，啲popo係向住車廂方向行入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Aqh49ca.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAqh49ca.png&h=c853999e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UhM096qHFkI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DUhM096qHFkI&d=Wg3pkMW64ksxbb%2FAt9Sry%2BxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=93dba59e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UhM096qHFkI</a><br />\n拍片者跟住搭返轉頭，影住架車飛埋九龍灣，片段開頭隱約見到個時間係21:12，離觀塘線全停仲有一段時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 10 月 4 日觀塘站，係被popo自己縱火時序分析：<br />\n7:50 立場新聞 live 影到示威者破壞完再逃走，返轉頭再影站內情況，服務站依然完好,之前示威者只是敲爛東西，完全無用火的東西，甚至有用消防喉射水意圖破壞電子設施，效果是更難起火。<br />\n9:00 有市民影到觀塘站已經有防暴<br />\n10:17 地鐵宣布關站<br />\n10:30 消防正在撲火<br />\n<br />\n<strong>綜合拍片者同明報新聞，當晚時序分析：<br />\n19:50 觀塘封站<br />\n21:00 九龍灣封站<br />\n21:03 popo上咗觀塘月台 (21:00呢個時間的確有popo喺觀塘站出現)<br />\n21:12前 運popo的列車已經離開觀塘站<br />\n21:51 觀塘線全停</strong><br />\n<br />\n利申：唔係想幫黨鐵或popo，大家要再fact check一下觀塘站當晚邊個燒到爙晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffc17a06b98cde33324d016ec535ee4fc1bb70ba","tid":1658820,"uid":71508,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T15:41:48.000Z","msg":"一定係<br />\n冇炒車"},{"pid":"3893566418c912da2998f6ca8379ed8442a03ff0","tid":1658820,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T15:42:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76cdd2dc9efa9127c3304fbd44ae497ea4eb4596","tid":1658820,"uid":321848,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T15:43:08.000Z","msg":"係呀；呀sir 一定係示威者做；<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />；sir 重有無多d片"},{"pid":"9851373a8ec92af4bc74a6ea4317af116aae726b","tid":1658820,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76cdd2dc9efa9127c3304fbd44ae497ea4eb4596","tid":1658820,"uid":321848,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T15:43:08.000Z","msg":"係呀；呀sir 一定係示威者做；<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />；sir 重有無多d片"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T15:48:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a00380dd57d087a1424a94bc4271d9aa1675e27","tid":1658820,"uid":168449,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"c